'''Moosa Manik''' is a Maldivian film actor.
==Career== He was also part of the Mohamed Musthafa Hussain's critically acclaimed film ''[[Nufolhey Maa]]'' which focuses on a love triangle between a doctor, nurse and patient.<ref name=legend>{{cite news|url=https://avas.mv/18215 |title=Born to be a legend |language=Divehi|work=Avas |last=Nadheem |first=Ahmed |date=6 June 2016 |archiveurl=http://archive.is/3BQlt |url-status=live|archivedate=18 May 2019 |accessdate=18 May 2019}}</ref> Apart from starring in the film as the father of a nurse who is forced to make a strenuous decision, Manik wrote the story of the film, developed the screenplay along with Hussain and penned lyrics for the songs.<ref name=legend/>
