The following year, he starred in Ali Shameel's drama film ''[[Hithi Nimun]]'' (2001) opposite [[Mohamed Shavin]], [[Mariyam Nisha]] and [[Sheereen Abdul Wahid]], which follows the storyline of a stubborn young man who abandons his girlfriend when he discovers about her pregnancy.<ref name=Top10Actresses/>
